### Instructions:
### 1. Install the "REST Client" extension for VS Code (id: humao.rest-client).
### 2. You will see "Send Request" clickable links above each URL.
### 3. Click "Send Request" to test the endpoint.
### 4. Ensure your backend is running (`uvicorn main:app --reload`).

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Root Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### ---------------- INTERVIEW ----------------

### Start Interview
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/interview/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "interviewType": "Technical",
  "jobRole": "Frontend Developer"
}

### Answer Question
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/interview/answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "replace-with-uuid",
  "userId": 1,
  "answer": "I use React and TypeScript.",
  "questionNumber": 0
}

### Teach Me
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/interview/teach-me
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "replace-with-uuid",
  "questionNumber": 0,
  "question": "Tell me about yourself.",
  "userAnswer": "I am a dev."
}

### Save Result
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/interview
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 1,
    "communicationScore": 85,
    "confidenceScore": 90,
    "relevanceScore": 80,
    "feedback": "Great job"
}

